\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces The regulatory cycle with sequential BIND-remeasure-VEIL protocol. The evaluator measures coordination and gatedness, fires BIND if coordination is low, \textbf  {remeasures}, then fires VEIL if gatedness is high. This prevents destructive interference.}}{6}{figure.caption.13}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:regulatory}{{3}{6}{The regulatory cycle with sequential BIND-remeasure-VEIL protocol. The evaluator measures coordination and gatedness, fires BIND if coordination is low, \textbf {remeasures}, then fires VEIL if gatedness is high. This prevents destructive interference}{figure.caption.13}{}}
